data.description: Charming tri-level townhome at Esperto, in the highly sought-after Valencia West Creek Community. Well-maintained, beautifully manicured courtyard and welcoming entry. The home features brand-new laminate flooring and all-new interior paint. The living and dining room has a door that leads out to the balcony where you can sit and enjoy your morning coffee or a glass of wine at the end of the day. The dining room also features a brand new decorator light fixture. The kitchen has granite countertops, maple-finish cabinetry, and a convenient breakfast bar. A stainless steel refrigerator is included. A full bathroom and in-closet laundry with a washer and dryer conveniently located in the hallway. The secondary bedroom has its own private floor space with a full-sized closet.  Top floor stairs leading to a mini loft adjacent to the primary bedroom which is perfect for a home office or a great place to do their homework. The large primary bedroom has a spacious walk-in closet, an ensuite bathroom with dual sinks, and a separate shower tub. You’ll find a garage door upon entry, 2-car tandem direct access, and a desirable storage space. This property is located near award-winning schools. There are amazing community amenities including a stunning clubhouse that can be used for private events, 3 swimming pool & spa areas. Access to all West Creek ,West Hills community areas. Multiple access points to community park, miles of walking trails and bike paths,  and playgrounds. Easy access to the 5 freeway. Great place to call home!
